{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id42c300c3-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"358"},"text":"§ 358.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Basis to distributees","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300c4-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" General rule","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of an exchange to which section 351, 354, 355, 356, or 361 applies—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300c5-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Nonrecognition property","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The basis of the property permitted to be received under such section without the recognition of gain or loss shall be the same as that of the property exchanged—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300c6-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" decreased by—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id42c300c7-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the fair market value of any other property (except money) received by the taxpayer,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id42c300c8-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of any money received by the taxpayer, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id42c300c9-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1/A/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of loss to the taxpayer which was recognized on such exchange, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300ca-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" increased by—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id42c300cb-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount which was treated as a dividend, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id42c300cc-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/1/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of gain to the taxpayer which was recognized on such exchange (not including any portion of such gain which was treated as a dividend).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300cd-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Other property","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The basis of any other property (except money) received by the taxpayer shall be its fair market value.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300ce-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Allocation of basis","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300cf-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Under regulations prescribed by the Secretary, the basis determined under subsection (a)(1) shall be allocated among the properties permitted to be received without the recognition of gain or loss.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d0-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Special rule for section 355","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of an exchange to which section 355 (or so much of section 356 as relates to section 355) applies, then in making the allocation under paragraph (1) of this subsection, there shall be taken into account not only the property so permitted to be received without the recognition of gain or loss, but also the stock or securities (if any) of the distributing corporation which are retained, and the allocation of basis shall be made among all such properties.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d1-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Section 355 transactions which are not exchanges","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this section, a distribution to which section 355 (or so much of section 356 as relates to section 355) applies shall be treated as an exchange, and for such purposes the stock and securities of the distributing corporation which are retained shall be treated as surrendered, and received back, in the exchange.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d2-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Assumption of liability","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d3-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Where, as part of the consideration to the taxpayer, another party to the exchange assumed a liability of the taxpayer, such assumption shall, for purposes of this section, be treated as money received by the taxpayer on the exchange.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d4-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exception","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Paragraph (1) shall not apply to the amount of any liability excluded under section 357(c)(3).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d5-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exception","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This section shall not apply to property acquired by a corporation by the exchange of its stock or securities (or the stock or securities of a corporation which is in control of the acquiring corporation) as consideration in whole or in part for the transfer of the property to it.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d6-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"f"},"text":"(f)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definition of nonrecognition property in case of section 361 exchange","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this section, the property permitted to be received under section 361 without the recognition of gain or loss shall be treated as consisting only of stock or securities in another corporation a party to the reorganization.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d7-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/g"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"g"},"text":"(g)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Adjustments in intragroup transactions involving section 355","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of a distribution to which section 355 (or so much of section 356 as relates to section 355) applies and which involves the distribution of stock from 1 member of an affiliated group (as defined in section 1504(a) without regard to subsection (b) thereof) to another member of such group, the Secretary may, notwithstanding any other provision of this section, provide adjustments to the adjusted basis of any stock which—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d8-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/g/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is in a corporation which is a member of such group, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300d9-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/g/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is held by another member of such group,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"to appropriately reflect the proper treatment of such distribution.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id42c300da-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"h"},"text":"(h)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Special rules for assumption of liabilities to which subsection (d) does not apply","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300db-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"If, after application of the other provisions of this section to an exchange or series of exchanges, the basis of property to which subsection (a)(1) applies exceeds the fair market value of such property, then such basis shall be reduced (but not below such fair market value) by the amount (determined as of the date of the exchange) of any liability—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300dc-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" which is assumed by another person as part of the exchange, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300dd-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" with respect to which subsection (d)(1) does not apply to the assumption.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300de-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exceptions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided by the Secretary, paragraph (1) shall not apply to any liability if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300df-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the trade or business with which the liability is associated is transferred to the person assuming the liability as part of the exchange, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300e0-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" substantially all of the assets with which the liability is associated are transferred to the person assuming the liability as part of the exchange.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id42c300e1-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s358/h/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Liability","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this subsection, the term “liability” shall include any fixed or contingent obligation to make payment, without regard to whether the obligation is otherwise taken into account for purposes of this title.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id42c300e2-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736"},"text":"Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68A/117"},"text":"68A Stat. 117","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/866/tI/s21/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–866, title I, § 21(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"Sept. 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/72/1620"},"text":"72 Stat. 1620","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/621/s2/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–621, § 2(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-10-22"},"text":"Oct. 22, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/1311"},"text":"82 Stat. 1311","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/253/s1/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–253, § 1(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-03-31"},"text":"Mar. 31, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/296"},"text":"90 Stat. 296","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/tXIX/s1906/b/13/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, title XIX, § 1906(b)(13)(A)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-04"},"text":"Oct. 4, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1834"},"text":"90 Stat. 1834","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/600/tIII/s365/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–600, title III, § 365(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-11-06"},"text":"Nov. 6, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/2855"},"text":"92 Stat. 2855","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/647/tI/s1018/d/5/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–647, title I, § 1018(d)(5)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/3580"},"text":"102 Stat. 3580","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/508/tXI/s11801/c/8/G"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–508, title XI, § 11801(c)(8)(G)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-05"},"text":"Nov. 5, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/1388-524"},"text":"104 Stat. 1388–524","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/34/tX/s1012/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–34, title X, § 1012(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-08-05"},"text":"Aug. 5, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/916"},"text":"111 Stat. 916","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/36/tIII/s3001/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–36, title III, § 3001(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", (d)(6), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-06-25"},"text":"June 25, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/182"},"text":"113 Stat. 182","children":[],"tail":", 184; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/554/s1/a/7/tIII/s309/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–554, § 1(a)(7) [title III, § 309(a)]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-12-21"},"text":"Dec. 21, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/2763"},"text":"114 Stat. 2763","children":[],"tail":", 2763A–638; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/147/tIV/s412/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–147, title IV, § 412(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-03-09"},"text":"Mar. 9, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/53"},"text":"116 Stat. 53","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id42c300e3-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id42c300e4-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id42c300e5-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2002—Subsec. (h)(1)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/147"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–147","children":[],"tail":" amended subpar. (A) generally. Prior to amendment, subpar. (A) read as follows: “which is assumed in exchange for such property, and”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2000—Subsec. (h). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/554"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–554","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (h)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1999—Subsec. (d)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/36"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–36","children":[],"tail":" struck out “or acquired from the taxpayer property subject to a liability” after “liability of the taxpayer” and “or acquisition (in the amount of the liability)” after “such assumption”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1997—Subsec. (g). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/34"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–34","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (g)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/508/s11801/c/8/G/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–508, § 11801(c)(8)(G)(i)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “or 361” for “361, 371(b), or 374”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/508/s11801/c/8/G/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–508, § 11801(c)(8)(G)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", struck out par. (3) “Certain exchanges involving ConRail” which read as follows: “To the extent provided in regulations prescribed by the Secretary in the case of an exchange to which section 354(d) (or so much of section 356 as relates to section 354(d)) or section 374(c) applies, for purposes of allocating basis under paragraph (1), stock of the Consolidated Rail Corporation and the certificate of value of the United States Railway Association which relates to such stock shall, so 